{"tid":245089,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【因...被剔除】國泰又有壞消息！被剔出MSCI香港指數 跌近4%","createTime":"2017-05-16T03:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T12:38:29.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c24c75a31f346775ab97931fb3d11ff7d28f6068","tid":245089,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/112004_de917f6042c53e6536646a9c7c50d831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F112004_de917f6042c53e6536646a9c7c50d831.jpg&h=251fba3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明晟MSCI公佈，全球ACWI指數會增加57隻股份，同時剔除28隻，其中國泰航空（293）將被剔除在MSCI香港指數。國泰今早曾跌半成，最新報10.4元，跌3.6%，暫時成交額7,250萬元。<br />\n<br />\n被斬倉的輝山乳業（6863）亦被剔除在MSCI中國指數。<br />\n<br />\n香港小型指數股份增加8隻，包括大快活（052）、中國金洋（1282）、太和控股（718）、鼎億集團（508）、天順證券（1141）、利寶閣（8102）、日成控股（3708）及五龍動力（378）。<br />\n<br />\n另外，MSCI中國指數將加入近期大熱的美圖（1357），另外還有敏實（425）、四環醫藥（460）。另外，除了輝山，中外運（598）及恒騰網絡（136）亦被剔除MSCI指數。<br />\n<br />\nMSCI中國A股指數新增39隻及剔除22隻股份，納入指數的股份包括廣汽集團、汽海味業及大唐國際發電。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56699163&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56699163%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170516&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=f4a605c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56699163%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170516&h=a8b23b6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56699163&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170516</a>"},{"pid":"955d3242a0e484aafc05730537cc505b073aa47f","tid":245089,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係東方！"},{"pid":"5b508f5d56